projects.name: StaffApp
projects.subtitle: StaffApp is an application for posting and taking shifts for rental workers. This app was made so that managers can easily post and follow open shifts at units within their organisation
projects.details:
I worked on StaffApp within a team of 5 developers. We we're tasked to develop an application to replace paper call lists. The project began as a school project for the company Entail. We also got the chance to work on the project through the summer.
I worked in the backend and frontend as well as the person in charge of information security. This project was a great opportunity for me to learn about working in a team and on a larger project.
